{"type":"article","id":16210,"title":"特区政府提醒海外华侨华人：不要回国（被品葱转载后，原作者已遭铁拳","uid":26126,"topics":[528,6437,2609,6603,5906],"contents":"PCSAR Government Notice: Chinese expats should not return to China<br>\n<br>\n目前，中国大陆新冠肺炎疫情形势仍然严峻，人道灾难频发。<br>\n特区政府提醒各位海外华侨华人同胞，不要轻信CCTV、人民日报关于新冠肺炎疫情的宣传，如无必要，切勿返回中国，以免横遭不测，提前去世。<br>\n<br>\n品葱特别行政区<br>\n行政长官 习明泽<br>\n2020年3月15日<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PLzcpz3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PLzcpz3.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PLzcpz3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wdd3NRm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wdd3NRm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wdd3NRm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/tFPIpo7.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tFPIpo7.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/tFPIpo7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/WHd0ifd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WHd0ifd.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WHd0ifd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ETHdbu7UEAAGYH0?format=jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ETHdbu7UEAAGYH0?format=jpg\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ETHdbu7UEAAGYH0?format=jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/aQlmXia.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aQlmXia.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/aQlmXia.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/z1UusTf.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/z1UusTf.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/z1UusTf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/xu_xia/status/1238696096781787136\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/xu_xia/status/1238696096781787136</a><br>\n武汉丽岛花园。劫匪以上门量体温为名入室杀害一名女财务，抢走她保管的公款60万元。因她未上报健康表，物业上门查看发现其遇害<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZOF4Zwb.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZOF4Zwb.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZOF4Zwb.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/l3bu1Sp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/l3bu1Sp.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/l3bu1Sp.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/mCT6lz9.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mCT6lz9.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mCT6lz9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/8p3SP5n.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8p3SP5n.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/8p3SP5n.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/HTlqTXw.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HTlqTXw.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/HTlqTXw.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<blockquote><b>如无必要，切勿返回中国，以免横遭不测，提前去世。</b></blockquote><br>\n扩展阅读：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/20753\">https://pincong.rocks/question/20753</a><br>\n<br>\n----<br>\n更新：已经出事了。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://preview.redd.it/m1ybkr0oium41.jpg?width=900&amp;format=pjpg&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=64cb9185df87f60de8c4abf18303bcb1f2dd0889\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://preview.redd.it/m1ybkr0oium41.jpg?width=900&amp;format=pjpg&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=64cb9185df87f60de8c4abf18303bcb1f2dd0889\" alt=\"https://preview.redd.it/m1ybkr0oium41.jpg?width=900&amp;format=pjpg&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=64cb9185df8